text: Mallory Jansen (born 18 June 1989) is an Australian actress. She co-starred as Madalena in the ABC series Galavant. She starred in the ABC Family sitcoms Baby Daddy and Young & Hungry. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian voice actors Category:Actors from Melbourne
